list.abstract: none，英语单词，可用作代词，指代某人或某物。也可作形容词、副词和名词，翻译为没有的、没有人、一个也不等。

yingyinNormal.en: Mr. Moon, none of your shows have ever worked. None of them! You've had your chances. Now, settle your accounts, or we will repossess this property. Okay. Toodle-oo.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你上演的剧目没有一个赚钱的，一个都没有！你有过偿还机会，现在请你立刻还款，否则我们将以你的剧院充抵债。好的，再见，慢走。

yingyinNormal.en: But losing my virginity to Chuck Bass? None of my friends will ever understand.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是把我的贞操给了巴特·拜斯？没有一个朋友会理解我的。

yingyinNormal.en: We'd try to join a frat. None of them would take us. We'd start our own. Oh, my God. That sounds amazing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一起进兄弟会，没有一个兄弟会愿意要我们，我们自己办一个，天呐，听起来太棒了。

yingyinNormal.en: And then tomorrow, you could have Christmas morning in your own houses. Which, by the way, none of you have invited me to.
yingyinNormal.zh: 然后明天，你们都可以在自己家里过节，顺便提一下，你们没有一个邀请我去。

yingyinNormal.en: And where can we go to listen to world pop? I don't think there's a world pop station or magazine, unfortunately there are none, there should be.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们可以去哪里听世界流行音乐呢？我认为没有一个世界音乐站，或者杂志，很遗憾没有，我觉得应该要有。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, none of the sane ones wanted to come back with me! That's not the point, okay? The point is you are the one who moved on and didn't tell anyone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 嘿，正常的人没有一个要跟我回来！这不是重点好吗？重点是你抛下我们的过去，而你却没有说。

yingyinNormal.en: None of my shoes fit me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的鞋都不能穿了。

yingyinNormal.en: Pepper? None for me. Okay sorry.
yingyinNormal.zh: 胡椒？我不用。好，对不起。

yingyinNormal.en: None of that's your fault, Steve.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这不是你的错，史蒂夫。

yingyinNormal.en: None of your business, that's why.
yingyinNormal.zh: 原因就是，关你屁事。

yingyinNormal.en: Something none of your ancestors learned.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的先人们都没有做到这一点。

yingyinNormal.en: Do you not have any? Well, none I know of.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你难道没有缺点嘛？我想不出来有什么啊。

yingyinNormal.en: The surprising answer is none of the above!
yingyinNormal.zh: 出乎意料的，是以上皆非。

yingyinNormal.en: The surprising answer is none of the above!
yingyinNormal.zh: 出乎意料的，是以上皆非。

yingyinNormal.en: You're losing clients. None of that is true.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你在流失客户。那些都不是真的。

yingyinNormal.en: But none of them have made me look ordinary.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但我还是没法变成普通人那样。

yingyinNormal.en: You know that none of that is made in America.
yingyinNormal.zh: 要知道这些都不是美国产的。

yingyinNormal.en: She's right, Serena. I mean, none of us are saints.
yingyinNormal.zh: 瑟琳娜，她说的对，这儿没有谁是圣人。

yingyinNormal.en: But none of this explains why I couldn't cross over.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这些都不能解释我为什么过不了桥。

yingyinNormal.en: None taken. Although "repellent" is kind of a strong word.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我没在意，虽然“厌恶”这词儿有点重了。

word_usage.usage:
①none作不定代词可代替可数名词，也可代替不可数名词。代替不可数名词作主语时，谓语动词用单数；代替可数名词作主语时，若侧重于整体，谓语动词用单数；若侧重于每个个体，谓语动词则用复数。如：
None of the drivers has/have turned up.
司机们一个都没来。
② none指人或物，可接of短语；no one与nobody 只指人，不按of短语。
③ 回答how many/how much时用none ；回答who时 用no one。如：
—How much money do you have with you?  —None.
—你身上带了多少钱？—一分钱也没带。
—Who is in the classroom right now?  —None. 
—现在谁在教室里？—没人。
